<subSubSection pageId="3" pageNumber="32" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="3.[151,1436,844,1952]" pageId="3" pageNumber="32">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[198,340,1771,1797]" pageId="3" pageNumber="32">Discussion:</emphasis>
The male imago of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Dominguez, Molineri &amp; Mariano" authorityYear="2009" box="[617,823,1772,1797]" class="Insecta" family="Leptophlebiidae" genus="Askola" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ephemeroptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="32" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="paprockii" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis box="[617,823,1772,1797]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="32">Askola paprockii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis bold="true" box="[838,940,1771,1797]" pageId="3" pageNumber="32">
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[838,940,1771,1797]" pageId="3" pageNumber="32" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
can be distinguished by the following combination of characters: 1) General coloration yellowish white with grayish marks (
<figureCitation box="[1170,1284,1810,1836]" captionStart="FIGURES 1–6" captionStartId="4.[151,272,1935,1959]" captionTargetBox="[252,1334,187,1911]" captionTargetId="figure-65@4.[252,1335,187,1911]" captionTargetPageId="4" captionText="FIGURES 1–6. Askola. Figs 1–3, Askola emmerichi, sp. nov., male imago. 1, general aspect, lateral view; 2, head, dorsal view; 3, head, lateral view. Figs 4–6, Askola paprockii sp. nov., male imago. 4, body, dorsal view; 5, idem, ventral view; 6, head, dorsal view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5319924" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5319924/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="32">Figs. 4–5</figureCitation>
), wings with grayish spots (
<figureCitation box="[327,418,1849,1875]" captionStart="FIGURES 25–36" captionStartId="10.[151,269,1901,1925]" captionTargetBox="[195,1385,727,1874]" captionTargetId="figure-302@10.[194,1393,727,1877]" captionTargetPageId="10" captionText="FIGURES 25–36. Askola. Figs 25–27, male fore wing: 25, Askola emmerichi sp.nov.; 26, Askola paprockii sp. nov.; 27, Askola cipoensis sp. nov. Figs 28–30, Askola emmerichi sp.nov.: 28, genitalia, ventral view; 29, genitalia, lateral view; 30, penes, detail. Figs 31–33, Askola paprockii sp. nov.: 31, genitalia, ventral view; 32, genitalia, lateral view; 33, penes, detail. Figs 34–36, Askola cipoensis sp. nov.: 34, genitalia, ventral view; 35, genitalia, lateral view; 36, penes, detail." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5319934" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5319934/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="32">Fig. 26</figureCitation>
); 2) dorsal portion of eyes grayish black, eyes widely meeting dorsally on meson of head (
<figureCitation box="[223,295,1888,1914]" captionStart="FIGURES 1–6" captionStartId="4.[151,272,1935,1959]" captionTargetBox="[252,1334,187,1911]" captionTargetId="figure-65@4.[252,1335,187,1911]" captionTargetPageId="4" captionText="FIGURES 1–6. Askola. Figs 1–3, Askola emmerichi, sp. nov., male imago. 1, general aspect, lateral view; 2, head, dorsal view; 3, head, lateral view. Figs 4–6, Askola paprockii sp. nov., male imago. 4, body, dorsal view; 5, idem, ventral view; 6, head, dorsal view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5319924" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5319924/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="32">Fig. 6</figureCitation>
); 3) 4 costal cross veins from bulla to costal brace (
<figureCitation box="[906,995,1888,1914]" captionStart="FIGURES 25–36" captionStartId="10.[151,269,1901,1925]" captionTargetBox="[195,1385,727,1874]" captionTargetId="figure-302@10.[194,1393,727,1877]" captionTargetPageId="10" captionText="FIGURES 25–36. Askola. Figs 25–27, male fore wing: 25, Askola emmerichi sp.nov.; 26, Askola paprockii sp. nov.; 27, Askola cipoensis sp. nov. Figs 28–30, Askola emmerichi sp.nov.: 28, genitalia, ventral view; 29, genitalia, lateral view; 30, penes, detail. Figs 31–33, Askola paprockii sp. nov.: 31, genitalia, ventral view; 32, genitalia, lateral view; 33, penes, detail. Figs 34–36, Askola cipoensis sp. nov.: 34, genitalia, ventral view; 35, genitalia, lateral view; 36, penes, detail." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5319934" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5319934/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="32">Fig. 26</figureCitation>
); 4) forceps whitish except basal half washed with gray (
<figureCitation box="[373,444,1926,1952]" captionStart="FIGURES 1–6" captionStartId="4.[151,272,1935,1959]" captionTargetBox="[252,1334,187,1911]" captionTargetId="figure-65@4.[252,1335,187,1911]" captionTargetPageId="4" captionText="FIGURES 1–6. Askola. Figs 1–3, Askola emmerichi, sp. nov., male imago. 1, general aspect, lateral view; 2, head, dorsal view; 3, head, lateral view. Figs 4–6, Askola paprockii sp. nov., male imago. 4, body, dorsal view; 5, idem, ventral view; 6, head, dorsal view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5319924" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5319924/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="32">Fig. 5</figureCitation>
); 5) penes not extending beyond posterior margin of styliger plate (
<figureCitation box="[1236,1380,1926,1952]" captionStart="FIGURES 25–36" captionStartId="10.[151,269,1901,1925]" captionTargetBox="[195,1385,727,1874]" captionTargetId="figure-302@10.[194,1393,727,1877]" captionTargetPageId="10" captionText="FIGURES 25–36. Askola. Figs 25–27, male fore wing: 25, Askola emmerichi sp.nov.; 26, Askola paprockii sp. nov.; 27, Askola cipoensis sp. nov. Figs 28–30, Askola emmerichi sp.nov.: 28, genitalia, ventral view; 29, genitalia, lateral view; 30, penes, detail. Figs 31–33, Askola paprockii sp. nov.: 31, genitalia, ventral view; 32, genitalia, lateral view; 33, penes, detail. Figs 34–36, Askola cipoensis sp. nov.: 34, genitalia, ventral view; 35, genitalia, lateral view; 36, penes, detail." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5319934" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5319934/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="32">Figs. 31–32</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
